<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/90807300-evan-o">Evan O</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Absolutely it is for adults and children. I read this to my kids every year at Christmas, and I read it to myself even when they are not around. It is<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Absolutely it is for adults and children. I read this to my kids every year at Christmas, and I read it to myself even when they are not around. It is a beautiful poem full of meaning and wit. you will discover new beauty in it every year. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
