  <span id="freeText1938326305241339030" style="display:none">I've meant to read this for a long time. The long wait did not lead to disappointment. A wonderfully descriptive short story about family visiting, meals cooked and emotions felt on Christmas day. Ardizzone's illustrations made this lovely account wonderful.</span>
