          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2213937966" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2303859617951287619">Classic memories of Christmas from a bygone era. Oh what fun! Thomas did radio performances and recorded this in 1952; it was published in book form in 1954. This edition was beautifully illustrated by Trina Schart Hyman.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


