<div id="review_1940448847" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1940448847" />
    <a title="Linda " class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3919132-linda"><img alt="Linda " src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1507125560p2/3919132.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1940448847?book_show_action=true">Mar 13, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Linda " class="user" itemprop="url" name="Linda " href="/user/show/3919132-linda">Linda </a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3919132-linda?shelf=awesome-pictures">awesome-pictures</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3919132-linda?shelf=childrens-books-that-adults-can-rea">childrens-books-that-adults-can-rea</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3919132-linda?shelf=action-and-or-adventure">action-and-or-adventure</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3919132-linda?shelf=children-s-picture-books">children-s-picture-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3919132-linda?shelf=1920s-time-period">1920s-time-period</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3919132-linda?shelf=setting-is-wales">setting-is-wales</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1940448847" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10915935426559286700">I understand <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/563820.A_Child_s_Christmas_in_Wales' title='A Child&apos;s Christmas in Wales by Dylan Thomas' rel='nofollow noopener'>A Child&apos;s Christmas in Wales</a> was first published in 1954 and a year after the author&apos;s death. It was based on his childhood exploits while growing up. Mr Thomas&apos;s words easily lulled the reader into an innocent past. <br/><br/>On its own, I would have given the story 3 1/2 stars but my copy was the slim hardback with pictures drawn by Trina Schart Hyman. <b>I loved her illustrations</b>. Some were in black and white, others were in color. As I watched, the story took on a life of its own. <br/><br/>Cigars and</span>
  <span id="freeText10915935426559286700" style="display:none">I understand <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/563820.A_Child_s_Christmas_in_Wales" title="A Child's Christmas in Wales by Dylan Thomas" rel="nofollow noopener">A Child's Christmas in Wales</a> was first published in 1954 and a year after the author's death. It was based on his childhood exploits while growing up. Mr Thomas's words easily lulled the reader into an innocent past. <br /><br />On its own, I would have given the story 3 1/2 stars but my copy was the slim hardback with pictures drawn by Trina Schart Hyman. <b>I loved her illustrations</b>. Some were in black and white, others were in color. As I watched, the story took on a life of its own. <br /><br />Cigars and elderberry wine, ice cream hills and the crackling sea became real. Cats and dogs were everywhere. The visiting uncles and aunties with all their inflections and oddish absurdities opened a window to a time-gone-by. I thought more than once, where was mum and dad? And I wondered how much of what Dylan wrote was true and formed the man he would eventually become. <br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="10915935426559286700" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


