        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2204646951" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1307062119318991530">A poetic novella of Christmas reminiscences as a young boy, beautifully written and exquisitely illustrated. The illustrations really lift this above the ordinary cute holiday tale.</span>

